IIRC negative numbers for the custom diplay lines means to allocate that 
much space per line. So in your example of -4, you can have 4 copper 
instructions per line.

And also IIRC each colour change needs 4 copper instructions for AGA. So 
you would only be able to make 1 colour change per line unless you multiply 
by the number of changes per line.

